{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99713-xiaoxin-laohu-laile","title":"小心！ 老虎来了！","description":"当老虎穿过森林时，每只动物都会知道！ 听取警告大家老虎已经到了个样的警报声。","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Rohan Chakravarty"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99713-xiaoxin-laohu-laile"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/495589/size3/0ffeaffc8b06617aca654bbe2fa9542b.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/495589/size6/0ffeaffc8b06617aca654bbe2fa9542b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48378/size6/d6762057368d196d85e6659c017ed4a3.jpg","text":"做老虎不容易。\n是的，老虎很美，也很凶。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48379/size6/e7d4148f8437a720ddb0e115ddd21b64.jpg","text":"但是老虎也又大又重。\n因为这样，他们寻找食物很困难。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48380/size6/dd66a1cfaccef0a7b72696b9d42a65a3.jpg","text":"老虎每20次捕猎，\n只能吃一次。","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48381/size6/dc1adfd806cace6969c6a3c2b446ca7b.jpg","text":"老虎穿过森林时，\n轰！ 啪！ 砰！\n猴子的叫声，就像一个老人在咳嗽！\n轰！ 啪！ 砰！","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48901/size6/48e24ba81e63bc56a70a994095150e2d.jpg","text":"嚎! 嚎!\n吠叫鹿的叫声，像一只害怕的狗！\n嚎! 嚎!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48902/size6/400d34cd99255ab56c87c33b189fde25.jpg","text":"喔！ 喔！ 喔！\n斑点鹿的叫声，像一只小鸟！\n喔！ 喔！ 喔！","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48905/size6/49c768d7866a991b3291cb47ecd2d1aa.jpg","text":"整片森林都知道老虎已经来了！\n吼? 吼?\n老虎想知道，大家都去了哪里？","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":30}}